title: The Mike Rosen Radio Show NOV-27-2013 WED
description:
The Mike Rosen Radio Show NOV-27-2013 WED




Wednesday, November 27, 2013



Interview With Scott Walker

 
 

 - 9AM hour

Guest: Denver Mayor,
      Michael Hancock answers listeners' questions during his monthly visit with Mike.




 - 10AM hour

1. Guest: Colorado Secretary of State,
      Scott Gessler talking about the legal and electoral ramifications
        of the resignation of state senator, Evie Hudak 
          prior to a possible recall election. 

2. Guest: Colorado political analyst, Kelly Maher talks about the resignation of Evie Hudak.




 - 11AM hour

1. Guest: Scott Walker, Governor of Wisconsin - 
    "Unintimidated: A Governor's Story and a Nation's Challenge."

2. Today Show account of "knockout" incident fails to mention
      victim successfully defended himself with a concealed carry gun.
